metadata.name: MONART NFT BARCELONA RARITIES #1
metadata.description:
Monart NFT is a descriptive project that establishes a connection between physical and digital art.

10 renowned artists from each city starting in Barcelona, then Paris, Berlin, Milan, and New York paint 5 physical works showing their point of view about Mona Lisa and their city.

This artworks are digitized by adding digital design elements called rarities to give them more exclusivity within the collection, all of them referring to events in the life of the Mona Lisa painting and the city of the collection.
